| Method      | Description                                            |
| ----------- | ------------------------------------------------------ |
| `isalpha()` | Check if all characters are letters (a-z, A-Z)         |
| `isdigit()` | Check if all characters are digits (0-9)               |
| `isalnum()` | Check if all characters are letters or digits          |
| `isupper()` | Check if all letters are uppercase                     |
| `islower()` | Check if all letters are lowercase                     |
| `isspace()` | Check if all characters are spaces                     |
| `istitle()` | Check if string is in title case (e.g., "Hello World") |
